
GIT HELP !!

If you forget how a command works or want to learn about it's options, you can use Git's built-in help. 
This is the fastest way to get answers without leaving your terminal. 

> COMMANDS 
-- To view the manual page for a command 
   [ git help <command> ]
-- To see help for a command 
   [ git <command> --help ]
-- To see a quick summary of options 
   [ git <command> -h ]
-- To list all possible git commands 
   [ git help --all ]
-- To list guides and concepts 
   [ git help -g] 
